targets.query: SELECT "ep_progress" FROM "bike_dynamic_info" WHERE ("experiment" =~ /^$experiment$/ AND "is_train" = true) AND $timeFilter
SELECT "ep_progress" FROM "bike_dynamic_info" WHERE ("experiment" =~ /^$experiment$/ AND "is_train" = false) AND $timeFilter
SELECT * FROM "bike_station_usage" WHERE ("experiment" =~ /^$experiment$/ AND  "ep" = $episode  and "station" = '$station') AND $timeFilter
SELECT /.policy$/, "action" FROM "bike_q_value" WHERE ("experiment" = '$experiment' AND  "ep" = $episode AND "tick" = $action_tick) AND $timeFilter
